<p>

  <strong><em>Our Mission</em></strong> is simple, to create a way to contribute to the Banano ecosystem while also contributing to the betterment of the world, however small it may be. 
  We strive to become the first Banano Nano-Charity. 
  We hope that by combining community activities such as raffles and auctions with charity that we can make charity a truly enjoyable experience.
  </p>

 <p>
   We believe that charity shouldn't be made in large sums of money and bragged about as 'philanthropy' but rather many small amounts from everyone that wants to. This project's goal is to be completely community 
   reliant based on four major components
   </p>
    <div style="text-align: left;">
         <ol>
     <li>Accumulating bans for charity via community participation in weekly raffles</li>
